# Russian-first owner constitution

**Owner does not speak English well. All owner-facing UI MUST be Russian.**

English ONLY in collapsed secondary blocks:
- file paths, API routes, git hashes, internal identifiers

## Applies to

Roadmap, execution, live runtime, priorities, reviews, deployment, blockers,
validation, timeline, narration, cards, tooltips, errors, recovery, health labels.

## Command center

Primary surface: `/operations/command`

## Cursor narration

Always `[AION АКТИВЕН]` in Russian during work. Never appear silent — use `execution:heartbeat` or `execution:daemon`.

## Autonomous mode

No "what next?". Use `npm run execution:runtime-loop` (continuous) or `execution:autonomous-next`. Never idle after task. Escalate architecture via `review:request` only.
